								<div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 margin-bottom-20">
									<p>The Business Results form let's you document what the leadership team has set for the company's goals, and the key measurements used to gauge job performance that affects successful realization of those goals. There is always a direct correlation between company performance and individual performance. <span style="font-family:Orbitron">P.E.R.F.O.R.M.</span> makes it easier to see and manage that relationship.</p>
