									<p class="text-center"><strong>Don't forget, even the most basic one-time company set-up fee includes Cultivisor loading your list of all employee</strong></p>
									<p class="text-right">You build an employee's historical profile one change at a time over a long career, so the entire historical profile of an employee is available. Once you know your company's top performers, you can start to look at their backgrounds to identify common elements. If keeping the data is the first step to understanding, then easy access and use of it must be step two.</p>
