									<p>Developing a person's skills relies on exposing them to the right learning experiences. For this, you have to know what he/she has and hasn't experienced.</p>
									<p>One of the ways <span style="font-family:Orbitron">P.E.R.F.O.R.M.</span> keeps track of training efforts is from the perspective of the individual. The Employee Activities Registration form lets you register an employee for a learning experience, and see what other items are in his/her development future and past.</p>
